           'Loan_Amount_Term', 'Credit_History']

Conclusion¶

  1. Approx 31.27 % customers are not submitted loan, it is'nt good figure for bank.
  2. Ratio of Unmarried customers are more than ratio of married ones to not submitted loan.
  3. Ratio of Not graduate customers are more than ratio of graduate ones to not submitted loan.
  4. In rural area, defaulter ratio is highest.
  5. Credit_History is a very important variable because of its high correlation with Loan_Status therefor showind high Dependancy for the latter.
  6. The Logistic Regression algorithm is the most accurate: approximately 77%.
